column1: #Text=At least my candidacy is beginning to force some of these practices out in the open .
#Text=Maybe that 's a better result than the one experienced by bigger name candidates who had all the advantages and still failed .

#Text=In 2012 , several primary challengers to President Barack Obama including John Wolfe , Jr. , Randall Terry , and Keith Russell Judd all qualified for delegates , though they ultimately were not seated at the convention due to technicalities .
#Text=Given the money you are willing to spend on a campaign and your ability to adhere to the rules , do you regret not running in 2012 ?
#Text=De La Fuente quotes Einstein : " We cannot solve our problems with the same thinking we used when we created them .
